query:
SELECT m.workspace_id as "workspace_id!: Uuid"
               FROM merges m
               INNER JOIN repos r ON r.id = m.repo_id
               WHERE m.merge_type = 'pr'
                 AND m.pr_number = $1
                 AND r.name = $2
                 AND m.pr_status = 'open'
               ORDER BY m.created_at DESC
               LIMIT 1
